published on 2022-02-19T08:33:02Z

uh excuse the way it sounds lol i fuckin suck at mixing atleast drums actually came out good verse she appears to me in my dreams i want her now so i call her name then i wake up and she's not there soon she will be mine and i will be alright chorus everyday fucking sucks because I'm not happy cannot sleep cannot dream cuz you come back right to me I'm in pain cant complain all i do is think all day my minds a fog all day long please come back it wont go wrong verse she comes to me and tells me that she loves me i tell her back and tell her don't you ever leave she has to go oh no if you ever come back will you let me know? chorus everyday fucking sucks because I'm not happy cannot sleep cannot dream cuz you come back right to me I'm in pain cant complain all i do is think all day my minds a fog all day long please come back it wont go wrong
